1) Install UEDGE using pip
pip install forthon
pip install mppl
pip install uedge

Note: Detailed insructions in https://github.com/LLNL/UEDGE/wiki/1)-Obtaining-UEDGE-and-installing-with-Python


2) Install uedge_mvu tools
git clone ssh://git@github.com/umansky/uedge_mvu

Run the following command inside the directory containing setup.py:
pip install --editable . --user

Note: Detailed instructions in https://github.com/umansky/uedge_mvu/blob/master/README.md


3) Run the simulation doing:
cd uedgebox
python -i run2steady.py
